SyncState *

IMAPAccount namy.19@gmail.com
Host imap.gmail.com
User namy.19@gmail.com
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
PassCmd "/Users/yqrashawn/.asdf/shims/oauth2get google namy.19@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2

IMAPStore namy.19@gmail.com-remote
Account namy.19@gmail.com

MaildirStore namy.19@gmail.com-local
Path ~/mail/namy.19@gmail.com/
Inbox ~/mail/namy.19@gmail.com/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim


Channel namy.19@gmail.com-remote
Far :namy.19@gmail.com-remote:
Near :namy.19@gmail.com-local:
# create new mailboxes both sides
Create Both
# delete both sides
Expunge Both
# exclude everything under the internal [Gmail] folder, except the interesting folders
# Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail"
# Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "![Gmail]/All Mail"
# Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Chats"
# include everything
Patterns * [Gmail]* !deleted !Templates "!Deleted Messages" !Newton !RSS !RSS/* !Trash "![Gmail]/Spam" "![Gmail]/All Mail"
# sync changes both ways (read, archived, etc.)
Sync All
# Save the synchronization state files in the relevant directory
SyncState *

